  "title": "Car Mechanic",
  "description": "<p><strong>About Gain City</strong> </p><p>At Gain City, we’ve been delivering trusted expertise and quality solutions in consumer electronics, air-conditioning, and home appliances since 1981. As a household name in Singapore, we take pride in\nour strong customer focus, innovative spirit, and commitment to service\nexcellence. With a dynamic workforce and a network of stores and service\ncentres island wide, we offer a vibrant and growth-oriented environment where\nemployees are empowered to thrive, take ownership, and make a real\nimpact. </p><p><strong>About the Role</strong></p><p>We are seeking a skilled and dependable Mechanic to join our workshop team. In this\nrole, you will be responsible for performing troubleshooting, servicing, and\nminor repairs on trucks, ensuring all vehicles are maintained in safe working\ncondition. You will also take care of tools and equipment, while maintaining a\nclean and safe work environment. This position is ideal for someone with\nhands-on automotive experience and a strong focus on quality workmanship   </p><p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Perform troubleshooting on trucks faults on\n     mechanical/electrical systems.</li><li>Perform basic vehicle servicing and minor repair.</li><li>Maintain the tools and equipment well.</li><li>Perform proper housekeeping to keep working\n     area clean and safe.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Must possess a <a href=\"#\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Class 3\n     Singapore Driving License</a> (Class 3A and 3C not accepted)</li><li>At least a Professional Certificate/Nitec in\n     Automotive Technology or a former NTC 2/3 in Motor Vehicle Mechanics.</li><li>At least 2 years of working experience in the\n     truck service and repair.</li></ul><p><strong>Note:</strong></p><p>·       Only shortlisted candidates will be\nnotified.</p><p><strong>Work Location:</strong></p><p>·       Gain City Megastore at Sungei Kadut,\nSingapore</p><p>Free shuttle Bus from Choa Chu Kang MRT\n& Yew Tee MRT to Gain City Megastore @ Sungei Kadut</p>",
